                </para>
            </listitem>
            
            
            <listitem>
                <para> The request is processed.</para>
            </listitem>
            
            
            <listitem>
                <para>
                    Repose sends the request to the origin service.
                </para>
            </listitem>
            
            <listitem>
                <para>
                    The origin service processes the request.
                </para>
            </listitem>
            
            <listitem>
                <para>
                    The origin service returns the response.
                </para>
            </listitem>
            
            <listitem>
